# Recode non-adopters to 3000
diff_data$toa[is.na(diff_data$toa)] <- 3000

model1 <- glm(adopted ~ 
              + t0_33 
              + t33_49 
              + t50_74 
              + t75_99 
              + t100_130  
              + existence
              + lag_w_expo_culture 
              + w_expo_colony
              + lag_w_expo_trade
              + gdp10000
              + regime
              + atwar
              + 0,
      dat    = diff_data, 
      subset = (per <= toa), # - extremely important !
      family = binomial(link="logit"))
summary(model1)
